tutorial.text:
Help your witch reach the end! Your path might be blocked. Perhaps you can pick up a rock and walk across! It might take at least <b>4</b> rocks, though... I wonder how you could save some time and coding space.<p>Have you ever heard of loops? It lets you repeat the same actions. If you type <pre>let x = 0;
while(x < 3){
  witch.moveRight();
  x++;
}</pre> Your witch will walk right a total of 3 times. If you need a Hint, press Hint!</p><p>Your witch has some movement and helpful 'methods':</p><pre>Move Right: witch.moveRight()
Move Left:  witch.moveLeft()
Move Up:    witch.moveUp()
Move Down:  witch.moveDown()
Pick Up:    witch.pickUp()
Cast Spell: witch.castSpell()
</pre>
